subsubsection.p:
Adding the four sides,
\boxed{ \oint_{\partial R} -y\,dx+x\,dy=2ab. }
But
ab=\operatorname{Area}(R).
So
\boxed{ \oint_{\partial R} -y\,dx+x\,dy = 2\,\operatorname{Area}(R). }

